content:
Update existing care plans by adding new problems, goals, and interventions using predefined care plan templates. The OmniScript shows care managers new problems, goals, and interventions based on the care plan templates that they select. A comparative view of the recommended and current problems, goals, and interventions makes it easier to update care plans as needed.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise and Unlimited editions with Health Cloud. Users with the Care Plans Access permission set license can use this feature. When you update a care plan, you can have a single, comprehensive care plan for a patient, which makes it easier to monitor patient progress. Select Care Plan Templates as the method for updating the care plan in the Update Care Plan OmniScript.
title: Update Care Plans with Predefined Templates
